NOTICE

This repository is a public regeneration recipe for the OMOP MedCAT Silver
dataset. It intentionally excludes generated MIMIC-derived rows:
- data/01_raw/mimic-iv-note/
- data/03_processed/text_concept_dataset/medcat_silver_full_v1/text_concept_dataset.jsonl
- data/03_processed/text_concept_dataset/medcat_silver_full_v1/reports/summary.json
- medcat_omop_snomed_condition_cdb artifacts

The published content is limited to code, documentation, tests, and the
aggregate public manifest:
- docs/dataset/medcat_silver_full_v1_public_manifest.json

The `examples/` directory contains fabricated JSONL rows for schema inspection
only. These examples are not MIMIC-derived and are not part of the generated
private dataset.
